description: MultiQ International AB engages in the provision of digital signage and monitor solutions to various industries. The company is headquartered in Lund, Skane and currently employs 60 full-time employees.  The company specializes in the liquid crystal display (LCD) technology. The firm is engaged in the production and marketing of customized monitors, modules and systems solutions, which incorporate aluminum chassis and protective glass screens. In addition, It offers a range of accessories, such as kiosk stands, wall brackets and point of sale (POS) poles, technical solutions, as well as a service package. The firm's customers comprise entities active primarily in the banking, retail, industry, transportation, government and the gaming sector. Furthermore, the Company is a parent of MultiQ Products AB, MultiQ Technologies AB, MultiQ Media Solutions AB and Mermaid A/S, among others.
naics: Semiconductor and Other Electronic Component Manufacturing
